title: Former Wisconsin Congressmen to speak at UW Oshkosh (University of Wisconsin - Oshkosh)
text: ( Source : University of Wisconsin - Oshkosh ) Former Wisconsin Congressmen Tom Petri (R) and Dave Obey (D) will be at the University of Wisconsin Oshkosh Tuesday, Oct. 27 for the Wisconsin Civic Participation Tour at 6:30 p.m. in Sage Hall ,
